description:
Responsibilities

Prepare 2D technical CAD drawings, 3D knowledge is an advantage;
Independently handle full set of residential and commercial construction drawings;
Organise and prepare interior design presentation;
Follow up client's requirements and convert the leads into orders;
Build and enhance customer relationship;
Liaise with internal parties to maximise sales performance and smooth operations;
Assist in other ad-hoc assignments as required;
Direct report to Sales Director.
Requirements

Diploma / Associate / Bachelor of Interior Design or equivalent;
Good command in AutoCAD, Sketch up and common office software;
Good presentation and communication skills;
Customer-oriented and responsible;
Self-motivated, hardworking, organised, outgoing;
Able to work under pressure and independently;
5-day work week on roster is required, including weekends;
Able to standby anytime in responding to customers;
Good command of Cantonese, Mandarin and English;
Immediate available is preferred.

Mitsubishi Electric Automation (Hong Kong) Ltd. specializes in diversified marketing and distribution services covering a host of sophisticated products in the core areas of industrial automation and electrical distribution & controls.  We are inviting high calibre professionals to apply for the following position:

SENIOR Sales engineer / Sales engineer             (Ref: SSE/SE/41/JD)

Job Description:

-              To assist in projects Spec in activities of PLC & VSD;

-              To explore new business opportunities e.g. contacting end-user, project consultants, contractors, switchboard makers, etc.

-              To assist in after sales service and technical solution of PLC & VSD;

-              To assist in product presentation to customers and communicate with suppliers;

-              Occasional business trip is required.

Job Requirement:

-              Higher Diploma holder or above;

-              Minimum 2 years relevant experiences, preferably in engineering industries;

-              Candidate with less experience will be considered for the position of Sales Engineer or Marketing Executive;

-              Good command of written and spoken Chinese, English & Mandarin;

-              Candidate with Certificate of REW Grade A or above is definitely an advantage;

Attractive remuneration package will be offered to the appointee.

Web Site: http://www.meah.com.hk

Project innovation planning, tendering and specification
Outgoing personality, good presentation skills, aggressive and well organize

Diploma or Degree holder



Benefits:    

Year-end performance bonus; 
Medical plan (Worldwide);
Birthday leave;
Exam leave;
Funeral leave;
Paternity leave;
MPF scheme;
Training & Development plan;
Staff purchase company product discounts.

Job Description

- Pre-sales support for sales/delivery of solutions to customers

- Responsible for cloud computing related technical support work;

- Participate in unified training from vendors;

Requirements

- Degree in Information Technology, Computer Science or related disciplines;

- Knowledge of any Cloud platform with experience in major areas like compute,

storage, backup and recovery, etc

- Knowledge and experience in related fields such as network, server, storage,

virtualization, cloud computing, disaster recovery and information security.

-Have a deep understanding of public cloud services and understand the products of

at least one public cloud provider.

- Possession of existing Cloud certificate is an advantage;

- Good presentation and interpersonal skills;

- Self-motivated, strong analytical and problem solving skills

- Proficient in both spoken and written English and Chinese;

- Fresh graduates will also be considered

The right person should have one of the following knowledge:

Server virtualization technology and common cloud computing framework;

Design and simple configuration of enterprise networking, load balancing, etc;

Relational database, such as mysql, redis;

Big data products, such as Hadoop, Spark, familiar with common big data construction solutions;

Cloud service system, including IaaS, PaaS, SaaS, with certain development and operation and maintenance experience.

We offer attractive remuneration and benefits, 5 days per week and on-the-job training to the qualified candidates.

Please send your application with full resume stating your present, expected salary and noticed period to the Company by clicking on the "Apply now".

Welcome to visit our Website at www.vestecs.com for Company information.
Personal data provided by applicants will be used strictly for recruitment purpose only.
